These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, eggplant, lettuce, broccoli
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
4. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the person eating broccoli is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
6. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person eating eggplant##5
7. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the person eating zucchini and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
8. the person eating eggplant and the owner of the rat have the same parity positions##9
9. the person eating lettuce and the owner of the ferret have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | zucchini | eggplant | lettuce     | broccoli |
| Pet           | hamster   | rat     | guinea-pig | ferret  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi, boat, van
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, sudoku, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is traveling and the person driving the taxi have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
6. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
7. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
8. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | van     | boat    | helicopter | taxi    |
| Hobby      | dancing | drawing | sudoku      | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta, milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, april, june, september
1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
2. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
8. the person drinking cola and the person who's birthday is in april have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | cola    | fanta   | coffee    | milk  |
| Food       | april | september | january | june |

