.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, hip-hop
City: nizza, berlin, san-francisco, hamburg
1. the fan country is not the person traveling to san-francisco##6
2. the person traveling to nizza and the fan blues have different parity positions##9
3. the person traveling to berlin and the fan classical have different parity positions##9
4. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
6. the fan classical is not the person traveling to berlin##6
7. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan classical##5
8. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the fan blues##1
9. the person traveling to hamburg is not the fan hip-hop##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | blues | country | hip-hop  | classical |
| Pet           | berlin   | nizza     | san-francisco | hamburg      |

