4. the american and the pilot have the same parity positions##9
5. the designer and the american have different parity positions##9
6. the indian is not to the left of the accountant##8
7. the thai is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5
8. the police-officer is not to the right of the thai##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | police-officer | accountant | pilot | designer |
| Nationality   | thai        | indian    | american   | brazilian |

