2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer and the person who likes aquamarine have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is not to the right of the person who likes chestnut##8
6. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
7. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | ivory    | mauve | aquamarine         | chestnut     |
| Sport         | sailing | soccer  | skateboarding | lacrosse |

