4. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
5. the person eating papaya is somewhere between the cape-cod house and the art-deco house##7
6. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
