2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
8. the person who's sport is rugby and the person drinking almond-milk have the same parity positions##9
9. the person who's sport is parkour and the person drinking sprite have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea   | fanta  | sprite  | almond-milk |
| Movie-Genre   | rowing | parkour | lacrosse | rugby      |

