.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, reading, gardening, board-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, jazz, r&b, soul
 1. the person who's hobby is reading and the fan r&b have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##8
 3. the fan blues is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
 4. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan r&b is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games and the fan jazz have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the fan soul##3
 9. the fan soul is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the fan blues##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | fishing  | board-games | gardening  | reading |
| Music-Genre   | soul | r&b     | blues | jazz     |

